  • Class
    Description
    AbstractBanknoteDispenser
    The abstract base class of devices that dispense banknotes.
    Banknote
    Instances of this class represent individual banknotes.
    BanknoteDispensationSlot
    Represents a banknote slot device that can dispense one or more banknotes, leaving them dangling until the customer removes it, via BanknoteDispensationSlot.removeDanglingBanknotes().
    BanknoteDispensationSlotObserver
    Observes events emanating from a banknote dispensation slot.
    BanknoteDispenserMR
    Represents a device that stores banknotes (as known as bills, paper money, etc.) of a particular denomination to dispense them as change.
    BanknoteDispenserObserver
    Observes events emanating from a banknote dispenser.
    BanknoteInsertionSlot
    Represents a simple banknote slot device that can either accept a banknote or eject the most recently inserted banknote, leaving it dangling until the customer removes it, via BanknoteInsertionSlot.removeDanglingBanknote().
    BanknoteInsertionSlotObserver
    Observes events emanating from a banknote slot.
    BanknoteStorageUnit
    Represents devices that store banknotes.
    BanknoteStorageUnitObserver
    Observes events emanating from a banknote storage unit.
    BanknoteValidator
    Represents a device for optically and/or magnetically validating banknotes.
    BanknoteValidatorObserver
    Observes events emanating from a banknote validator.
    IBanknoteDispenser
    The base type of devices that dispense banknotes.
